sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor U as Student
    participant FE as Next.js (Browser)
    participant MW as Next.js Middleware
    participant SB as Supabase Auth
    participant DB as Supabase DB (RLS)
    participant N8N as n8n

    U->>FE: Visit /dashboard
    FE->>MW: GET /dashboard
    MW->>SB: auth.getUser() (reads cookie)
    SB-->>MW: null (no session)
    MW-->>U: 302 → /auth/login?next=/dashboard

    U->>FE: Submit login form
    FE->>SB: signInWithPassword(email, password)
    SB-->>FE: Set-Cookie: sb-access-token, sb-refresh-token
    FE-->>U: 302 → /dashboard
    FE->>MW: GET /dashboard (with cookies)
    MW->>SB: auth.getUser() (refreshes if needed)
    SB-->>MW: User
    MW->>DB: SELECT FROM profiles WHERE id=auth.uid()
    DB-->>MW: Profile row (RLS pass)
    MW-->>FE: render <DashboardLayout/>
    FE-->>U: HTML

    Note over U,N8N: From here every server action goes through
    Note over SB: services that use the user's JWT, so RLS automatically
    Note over N8N: restricts data to the owner.

    U->>FE: Click "Enroll in this course"
    FE->>U: redirect to Stripe Checkout (course-level)
    U->>SB: (Stripe-hosted payment) — handled by Stripe
    SB->>N8N: checkout.session.completed (enrollment-created workflow)
    N8N->>DB: UPDATE enrollments SET status='active' + INSERT module_progress rows
    N8N-->>U: Confirmation email via Resend

    U->>FE: Pick a module inside the course
    FE->>N8N: (Calendly inline embed renders per module)
    N8N->>DB: INSERT module_bookings, INSERT meeting_links
    N8N-->>U: Confirmation email with Zoom join URL
